Tags:
  - 761
By: Sri Sankarâchârya
---
False notions cannot be negated in any way other than (thus knowing the Self).
It is these wrong notions that are the causes of delusion. These notions,
bereft of their cause (ignorance), come to an absolute end, like fire bereft of
fuel (when knowledge is achieved).
